{"tid":85531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"圖片報：沙比季尾掛靴","createTime":"2017-01-18T11:37:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T01:23:28.000Z","uid":4661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f041c6a6f3ac681a9f116062f7f91f61e7990687","tid":85531,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sports.now.com/sport/news/7/017/17101130017/17105634873_600x410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F7%2F017%2F17101130017%2F17105634873_600x410.jpg&h=4ec79bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=TMeNIT5X4VpCfFkda38KspkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=523996ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英國傳媒引述德國《圖片報》稱，前利物浦名將沙比阿朗素將在球季結束後掛靴。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》、《太陽報》周三引述德國《圖片報》稱，現時效力拜仁慕尼黑的前利物浦球星沙比阿朗素（Xabi Alonso）在今個球季結束後將高掛球靴。據悉，35歲的阿朗素在去年底與會方談及續約問題，他明確告訴球會完成合約後將退休。阿朗素2014年從皇家馬德里加盟，目前合約在季尾結束。<br />\n<br />\n阿朗素在皇家蘇斯達成名，2004年加盟利物浦，協助球隊奪得2004/05球季的歐聯冠軍；2009年轉投皇家馬德里，分別奪得西甲和歐聯冠軍；2014年加盟拜仁慕尼黑，取得德甲兩連冠。<br />\n<br />\n拜仁教練安察洛堤從來器重一班老將，日前才與荷蘭老將洛賓續約1年，新約至2018年屆滿；他同樣希望與阿朗素續約1年，但遭到對方拒絕。至於老國腳拿姆的合約至2018年屆滿，他將履行剩下的合約。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8668b898504b03ad11a087656769c396ef4316f0","tid":85531,"uid":4492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46e33b470059b533f0a5cd040a91a1f22174383","tid":85531,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmo